These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, bridge, monopoly, chess
The people have 4 different jobs:  paramedic, coach, journalist, librarian
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, boat, bus, ship
1. the person driving the airplane is the person playing chess##1
2. the person driving the bus is on the left of the coach##1
3. the person playing chess is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
5. the journalist is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3
6. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
7. the person driving the boat is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person driving the ship is between the librarian and the person playing mah-jongg##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Game         | chess      | mah-jongg | bridge | monopoly |
| Job   | journalist | paramedic  | coach   | librarian    |
| Transport     | airplane     | bus    | ship    | boat      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, singing, sudoku, video-games
There are 4 different favourite colors: amber, emerald, brown, orange
4 different pets are kept: cat, frog, guinea-pig, snake
1. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person who likes brown##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an even position##4
4. the owner of the cat is on the far right##1
5. the owner of the snake is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
7. the person who likes amber is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's hobby is singing##2
8. the person who likes orange is between the person who likes emerald and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | video-games | sudoku   | singing | dancing  |
| Color   | brown     | amber | orange  | emerald |
| Pet     | snake        | guinea-pig  | frog    | cat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, martial-arts, action, scientific
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, jazz, d&b, pop
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, roller, snowmobile, train
1. the fan of pop is between the person watching horror movies and the person watching scientific movies##2
2. the fan of jazz is the person driving the train##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is the person watching action movies##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
5. the person watching scientific movies is in an odd position##4
6. the fan of d&b is between the person watching martial-arts movies and the fan of reggae##2
7. the fan of pop is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre          | horror | martial-arts   | scientific     | action     |
| Music-Genre   | jazz  | pop | d&b   | reggae  |
| Transport     | train      | roller | snowmobile | motorbike |

