.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, horror, romance
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, poppy, iris, balloon-flower
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, card-games, photography, chess
1. the person who growsballoon-flower is in an even position##4
2. the person watching disaster movies is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
3. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
4. the person who growspoppy is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
5. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
6. the person watching horror movies is the person who growsmarigold##1
7. the person who growsiris is the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime  | romance   | horror     | disaster |
| Flower   | iris  | balloon-flower      | marigold        | poppy     |
| Hobby         | photography | skydiving | chess | card-games   |

