.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, red, lilac, pink
City: london, rome, paris, san-francisco
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, helicopter, jet-ski, van
1. the person who likes pink is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
2. the person who likes lilac is in an odd position##4
3. the person driving the bus is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
5. the person driving the bus is in an even position##4
6. the person traveling to rome is on the far left##1
7. the person who likes red is on the far right##1
8. the person who likes lilac is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
9. the person traveling to london is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Color   | white   | pink   | lilac | red |
| City         | rome      | san-francisco | london      | paris |
| Transport     | helicopter | bus        | van       | jet-ski  |

