.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, indie, trance, salsa
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, fishing, sudoku, woodworking
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, mexican, russian, japanese
1. the fan of indie is in an odd position##4
2. the russian is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
3. the egyptian is the fan of indie##1
4. the fan of trance is on the left of the mexican##1
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far right##1
6. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of indie##1
7. the fan of salsa is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre    | trance   | salsa      | indie       | techno |
| Hobby   | camping | woodworking | sudoku     | fishing |
| Nationality     | japanese     | mexican  | egyptian | russian |

