.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: lilac, ebony, turquise, blue
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, indian, italian, egyptian
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goat, guinea-pig, horse
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is the canadian##1
2. the owner of the goat is between the egyptian and the owner of the chinchilla##2
3. the egyptian is the person who likes ebony##1
4. the indian is on the left or right of the person who likes ebony##3
5. the person who likes lilac is in an even position##4
6. the egyptian is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
7. the canadian is the person who likes lilac##1
8. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Color      | turquise   | blue          | ebony | lilac        |
| Nationality   | italian     | indian | egyptian   | canadian     |
| Pet           | chinchilla | goat         | horse         | guinea-pig |

