.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, collecting, drawing, singing
4 different games are played: canasta, whist, billiard, monopoly
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, january, november, july
1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
2. the person playing billiard is the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the person playing monopoly is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
4. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
5. the person who's birthday is in january is between the person playing canasta and the person who's hobby is chess##2
6. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
7. the person who's hobby is chess is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person who's hobby is drawing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | collecting | chess      | drawing       | singing    |
| Game           | whist  | billiard  | monopoly | canasta |
| Birthday   | july      | november | january         | march    |

