.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, boat, jet-ski, skateboard
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, manager, pilot, social-worker
City: edinburgh, hannover, venice, boston
1. the entrepreneur is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
3. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
4. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
5. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person traveling to venice##3
6. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
7. the entrepreneur is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
8. the manager is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
9. the social-worker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Transport   | boat         | scooter  | jet-ski     | skateboard         |
| Job        | social-worker | manager | entrepreneur | pilot         |
| City      | hannover         | venice  | edinburgh   | boston |

