.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
There 4 different types of food: lime, artichoke, spinach, lettuce
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, malaysian, nigerian, turkish
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, motorbike, bike, jet-ski
 1. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the person eating spinach##3
 2. the canadian is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
 4. the nigerian is between the person eating artichoke and the person eating lime##2
 5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person eating artichoke##3
 6. the person driving the jet-ski is the person eating spinach##1
 7. the turkish is on the far right##1
 8. the person eating lime is in an odd position##4
 9. the malaysian is between the person eating lettuce and the person eating spinach##2
10. the person driving the bike is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food   | lime  | spinach    | artichoke | lettuce    |
| Nationality   | canadian | nigerian | malaysian  | turkish |
| Transport           | bike   | jet-ski    | snowmobile        | motorbike   |

