.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, juice, soy-milk
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, aconite, rose, zinnia
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, superhero, family, thriller
1. the person drinking 7up is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
3. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person who growsrose##3
4. the person who growsaconite is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
6. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
7. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
8. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person watching superhero movies##3
9. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage      | 7up                | soy-milk  | almond-milk | juice   |
| Flower           | zinnia | aconite | balloon-flower   | rose |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero         | time-travel     | thriller     | family |

