.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-12::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, biathlon, badminton, sailing
There are 4 different favourite colors: yellow, aquamarine, white, ivory
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, dubstep, jazz, r&b
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far left##1
3. the fan of dubstep is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3
4. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
5. the fan of d&b is between the person who likes ivory and the fan of r&b##2
6. the person who likes white is in an even position##4
7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Sport          | badminton    | biathlon  | sailing  | skateboarding |
| Color   | ivory | aquamarine | yellow | white |
| Music-Genre   | jazz    | d&b     | r&b    | dubstep |

