.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, water-polo, baseball, climbing
City: boston, colone, london, rome
4 different pets are kept: goat, horse, pony, turtle
1. the owner of the horse is between the person who's sport is baseball and the person traveling to boston##2
2. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person traveling to london is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
4. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
5. the owner of the turtle is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
7. the person traveling to boston is on the left or right of the person traveling to rome##3
8. the person traveling to london is the person who's sport is tennis##1
9. the person traveling to rome is between the owner of the pony and the owner of the goat##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Sport      | tennis | baseball      | water-polo  | climbing    |
| City   | london   | colone | rome | boston |
| Pet           | turtle      | pony       | horse   | goat      |

