.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, bluemaster, blend, vegafina
City: hamburg, miami, paris, berlin
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, golf, handball, lacrosse
1. the blend-smoker is in an even position##4
2. the bluemaster-smoker is between the vegafina-smoker and the person who's sport is cycling##2
3. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left or far right##3
4. the vegafina-smoker is in an even position##4
5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
6. the person traveling to berlin is between the person who's sport is cycling and the person traveling to hamburg##2
7. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
8. the person traveling to miami is in an even position##4
9. the person who's sport is cycling is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Cigar         | siglo    | blend | bluemaster  | vegafina  |
| City   | paris | miami       | berlin | hamburg |
| Sport         | handball   | cycling      | lacrosse | golf       |

