4. the person eating pepper is on the left or right of the chinese##3
5. the indian is between the person driving the bike and the person eating cherry##2
6. the person driving the airplane is the person eating grapes##1
7. the indian is on the left of the indonesian##1
8. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the indonesian##1

