.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-20::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, broccoli, lime, pomegranate
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, march, august, january
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, punk, pop, ambient
1. the person eating apple is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in january is in an odd position##4
3. the fan of trance is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3
4. the person eating lime is on the far left##1
5. the person eating broccoli is between the person who's birthday is in january and the person who's birthday is in december##2
6. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
7. the fan of pop is on the right of the person eating apple##1
8. the fan of punk is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food    | lime    | broccoli    | apple  | pomegranate |
| Birthday   | january | march | december | august      |
| Music-Genre     | punk   | trance        | ambient   | pop       |

 